channel.title: Comments on: STREAM: George Michael’s Version of New Order’s “True Faith”

item.title: By: Jonathan
item.dc:creator: Jonathan
item.description: Oddly enough, the auto-tune isn't as off-putting as its pairing with that adult contemporary / smooth r&b / laxative therapy background noise.
